show.description: Desperate for money, Chris never imagined he’d land in a fake marriage with a stranger who’s just as stubborn as he is. Between hospital bills, rent deadlines, and unexpected feelings, will this chaos lead to a real connection? Find out in "CEO’s Wife" a story of love born from struggle. Watch Now!
